## Implementation Notice

This is an ORIGINAL implementation of TFHE written from scratch in Go,
based on published academic research. This software:

- Does NOT use Zama's TFHE-rs, Concrete, or any third-party implementation
- Is built on github.com/luxfi/lattice (our own cryptographic primitives)
- Implements algorithms from peer-reviewed academic publications
- Contains novel optimizations developed independently by Lux Partners

Referenced academic works:
- Chillotti et al. "TFHE: Fast Fully Homomorphic Encryption Over the Torus" 
  (Journal of Cryptology, 2020)
- Ducas & Micciancio "FHEW: Bootstrapping Homomorphic Encryption in Less 
  Than a Second" (EUROCRYPT 2015)

